what we will cover?

* what is Bootstrap?
*Installation/Setup
*Grid System
*Components

what is Bootstrap?
- Most popular front-End framework
-Used for building responsive, mobile first websites and web applications
-HTML/CSS/JavaScript

why use Bootstrap?
-Increase development speed
-Assure responsiveness
-Prevent repetition between projects
-Add consistency
-Ensure cross browser compatibility
-Large community
-Customizable

Bootstrap components & helpers:

Alerts              List group              Spinners
Badges              Modal                   Toasts 
Breadcrumbs         Navbars                 Tooltips
Buttons             Panels                  Clearfix
Cards               Paginations             icons
Carousel            Popovers                Tables
Collapse            Progress bars           Responsive 
Dropdowns           Scrollspy               Gutters


Installation:
there are three ways:

1.download bootstrap from getbootstrap.com and extract the downloaded folder at the required location and 
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello Bootstrap World</h1>
    <script src="js/bootstrap.bundle.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

2.Installing via cdn
Go to https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/getting-started/download/ and copy and paste link and script tag same as below.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello CDN World!</h1>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>

3.npm installation
npm install bootstrap 
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet"
     href="node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello npm world!</h1>
    <script src="node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

to install bundle.js - npm install @popperjs/core --save
https://github.com/mdbootstrap/bootstrap-5-freecodecamp-source-code/blob/main/landing/.mdb

Bootstrap Breakpoints:
For laptops:
xxL-EXtra Extra Large >=1400px
xL-Extra Large 1200px min - 1399px max
Lg-large Screen 992px min - 1199x max
For tabs:
md-medium device 768px min - 991px max
sm-small device 576px min - 767px max
xs-Extra small device 0px min - 575px max


